<note id="fs-idm229130208" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm237541360"><emphasis effect="bold">Topics</emphasis>: 9.3 The End of the Cold War, 9.6 Challenges of the 21st Century</para>
<para id="fs-idm238644128"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm457889968"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objectives</emphasis>: Unit 9C Explain the causes and effects of the end of the Cold War and its legacy, Unit 9F Explain the causes and effects of the domestic and international challenges the United States has faced in the 21st century</para>
<para id="fs-idm232891504"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Developments</emphasis>: 9.3.I.C, 9.3.II.A</para>
<para id="fs-idm208171024"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-1 Developments and Processes, HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
